---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='About Us | Hancock Plastering & Painting Services' description='Family-run plastering and painting firm based in Harefield, Middlesex. City & Guilds certified, all work done in-house — no subcontractors.' activePage='about'>
<!-- HERO -->
<section style="position:relative;height:460px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(15).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 40%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 55%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 60px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / About</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,60px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Established trade.<br>Consistent finish.</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;line-height:1.5;">Harefield, Middlesex — serving the Home Counties since 2020.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STORY -->
<section style="padding:80px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:80px;align-items:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The company</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,36px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 28px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Founded on doing the job right. That hasn't changed.</h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 20px;">Hancock Plastering &amp; Painting Services was founded by Oliver Thomas Hancock, operating out of Harefield in Middlesex. What started as a sole-trade operation has grown into a team of four — all City &amp; Guilds certified, all directly employed by Hancock.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 20px;">Between the four of them, there's over 60 years of combined trade experience. Victorian terrace plaster, new-build skim, high-end Venetian finishing, external render for Home Counties properties — the team has done it all and keeps doing it properly.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">The growth goal is simple: more of the right customers. People who want the job done once, properly, at a fair fixed price. Not bargain hunters expecting contractor-grade work at DIY prices.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2px;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:24px;">
        <div style="aspect-ratio:1;overflow:hidden;">
          <img src="/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(2).webp" alt="Hancock tradesperson holding a steel trowel — branded workwear" title="Hancock tradesperson holding a steel trowel — branded workwear" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;">
        </div>
        <div style="aspect-ratio:1;overflow:hidden;">
          <img src="/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(15).webp" alt="Hancock Plastering branded van parked outside a residential property" title="Hancock Plastering branded van parked outside a residential property" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#F8FAFC;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:6px;padding:24px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#64748B;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 16px;">At a glance</p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;">
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;padding-bottom:12px;">
            <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#64748B;">Director</span>
            <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#0F172A;">Oliver Thomas Hancock</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;padding-bottom:12px;">
            <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#64748B;">Based</span>
            <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#0F172A;">Harefield, UB9 6HF</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;padding-bottom:12px;">
            <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#64748B;">Team size</span>
            <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#0F172A;">4 plasterers</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;padding-bottom:12px;">
            <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#64748B;">Qualifications</span>
            <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#0F172A;">City &amp; Guilds (all)</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;padding-bottom:12px;">
            <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#64748B;">Combined experience</span>
            <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#0F172A;">60+ years</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px;">
            <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#64748B;">Reviews</span>
            <a href="https://www.checkatrade.com/trades/HancockPlasteringandPaintingServices" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;text-decoration:none;">
              <div style="width:20px;height:20px;background:#00753A;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 11 11" fill="none"><path d="M1.5 5.5L4.5 8.5L9.5 2.5" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#00753A;">20+ on Checkatrade</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- USPS -->
<section style="padding:80px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">How we work</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,38px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 48px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">The same approach on every job.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:24px;">
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:#E0FAFF;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M2 9.5L2 14.5C2 15.05 2.45 15.5 3 15.5L15 15.5C15.55 15.5 16 15.05 16 14.5L16 6L11 2L3 2C2.45 2 2 2.45 2 3L2 9.5Z" stroke="#0F172A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M11 2L11 6L16 6" stroke="#0F172A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><line x1="5.5" y1="9.5" x2="12.5" y2="9.5" stroke="#0F172A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"></line><line x1="5.5" y1="12" x2="9.5" y2="12" stroke="#0F172A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"></line></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Fixed-price quote, in writing.</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The price is agreed before work starts. You'll have it confirmed in writing. No mid-job revisions, no ambiguity.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:#E0FAFF;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><circle cx="9" cy="9" r="7" stroke="#0F172A" stroke-width="1.5"></circle><path d="M9 5.5V9.5L12 11" stroke="#0F172A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">8am starts. Flexible scheduling.</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">We start at 8am and work around your project timeline. Developers and landlords — we understand you have other trades waiting.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:#E0FAFF;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M9 2L11 7H16.5L12.25 10.25L14 15.5L9 12.25L4 15.5L5.75 10.25L1.5 7H7L9 2Z" stroke="#0F172A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Deposit required upfront.</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">A deposit is required to book. This is standard practice for professional contractors and it's non-negotiable.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:#E0FAFF;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><rect x="2" y="5" width="14" height="10" rx="1.5" stroke="#0F172A" stroke-width="1.5"></rect><path d="M5 5V4C5 2.9 5.9 2 7 2H11C12.1 2 13 2.9 13 4V5" stroke="#0F172A" stroke-width="1.5"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">No subcontractors.</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Every job is done by the Hancock team. Nobody gets passed on to a third party you don't know and haven't vetted.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section style="padding:80px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,44px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.1;">Get your free quote today.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:17px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 40px;line-height:1.65;">Fixed price agreed before work starts. No surprises.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:32px 0 0;line-height:1.6;">Cancellations made less than 48 hours before your booking incur a £100 cancellation fee.</p>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
